01\/09\/dajjal-people-flee-to-mountains\/","url_meta":{"origin":6604,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dajjal: People flee False Messiah to the mountains","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Sharik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people will flee from the False Messiah into the mountains.\u201d She said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, where will the Arabs be on that day?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThey will be few.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u00a0Muslim 2945 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15721,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/20\/dajjal-tribulation-false-messiah-greatest\/","url_meta":{"origin":6604,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dajjal: No Fitnah greater than False Messiah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Imran ibn Husayn reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing between the creation of Adam until the establishment of the Hour is a greater tribulation than the False Messiah.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2946 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0650\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u064f\u0635\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"",